[07:40:34.413] [INFO ]     NovaAI provides a **one-time home office equipment stipend of $500 USD** for new hires. This stipend is issued **after the first month of employment** and requires submission of itemized receipts for eligible equipment purchases (e.g., monitors, keyboards, ergonomic chairs, desks, or essential peripherals). 
    
    The policy is formally documented in **"Remote Work and Equipment Stipend Policy v2.1"**, dated **January 15, 2023**. It applies to all new hires globally, regardless of role, and is non-taxable under U.S. IRS guidelines for qualified business expenses (subject to local tax laws in other jurisdictions). 
    
    *Note: Personal items (e.g., coffee makers, decorative items) or non-essential equipment are not covered. Reimbursement requests must be submitted via the company’s HR portal within 90 days of purchase.*
